131n m\u00F6ht\u0259\u015F\u0259m kolleksiyas\u0131n\u0131 k\u0259\u015Ff edin. Yeni burax\u0131l\u0131\u015Flar\u0131 oynay\u0131n, al\u0131n v\u0259 z\u00F6vq al\u0131n. Microsoft Store-da endirimli t\u0259klifl\u0259r.","Tencent.Page.Title":"MyApp Hub - Windows-da mobil proqramlar v\u0259 oyunlar endirin","Tencent.Page.Description":"Microsoft Store-da Tencent MyApp Hub-\u0131 ara\u015Fd\u0131r\u0131n \u2013 Windows-da \u0259n son mobil proqramlar v\u0259 oyunlar \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn t\u0259yinat yeri. \u0130ndi rahatl\u0131qla endirin!","Themes.Page.Title":"M\u00F6vzular - Windows T\u0259cr\u00FCb\u0259nizi F\u0259rdil\u0259\u015Fdirin","Themes.Page.Description":"Microsoft Store-da Windows i\u015F masas\u0131 t\u0259cr\u00FCb\u0259nizi f\u0259rdil\u0259\u015Fdirm\u0259k \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn m\u00F6vzular\u0131, divar ka\u011F\u0131zlar\u0131n\u0131 v\u0259 f\u0259rdil\u0259\u015Fdirm\u0259 se\u00E7iml\u0259rini k\u0259\u015Ff edin v\u0259 endirin.","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Title":"Komp\u00FCterinizi F\u0259rdil\u0259\u015Fdirin","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Subtitle":"Cihaz\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 \u00F6z\u00FCn\u00FCz\u0259 uy\u011Funla\u015Fd\u0131r\u0131n","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Description":"Windows-u se\u00E7ilmi\u015F m\u00F6vzu paketl\u0259ri il\u0259 f\u0259rdil\u0259\u015Fdirin - yeni divar ka\u011F\u0131zlar\u0131 v\u0259 vur\u011Fu r\u0259ngl\u0259ri","RankDisclosureIcon.Message":"S\u0131ralama meyarlar\u0131 haqq\u0131nda \u0259trafl\u0131 m\u0259lumat \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn bax\u0131n: {0}","RankDisclosureIcon.AutomationName":"S\u0131ralama a\u00E7\u0131qlamas\u0131","RankDisclosureIcon.HyperlinkText":"H\u00FCquqi bildiri\u015Fl\u0259r v\u0259 istehlak\u00E7\u0131 m\u0259lumatlar\u0131","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.Title":"\u00DCzr ist\u0259yirik","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.Description":"Bu veb-sayt\u0131n d\u00FCzg\u00FCn i\u015Fl\u0259m\u0259si \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn daha yeni brauzer\u0259 ehtiyac var.","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.About":"Microsoft Sto