n.","Collections.curated.halo-pc-games.Page.Description":"Halo PC oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-dan kampaniyalar, \u00E7oxoyun\u00E7ulu v\u0259 daha \u00E7ox \u015Feyl\u0259rl\u0259 Windows-da \u0259fsan\u0259vi elmi-fantastik at\u0131c\u0131l\u0131q fran\u015Fizas\u0131n\u0131 oynay\u0131n.","Collections.curated.space-pc-games.Page.Description":"Kosmos komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da Windows \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn elmi fantastika oyunlar\u0131nda qalaktikalar\u0131 ara\u015Fd\u0131r\u0131n, ulduz g\u0259mil\u0259rini idar\u0259 edin v\u0259 kosmosu f\u0259th edin.","Collections.curated.disney-pc-games.Page.Description":"Disney komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da sevimli Disney, Pixar, Marvel v\u0259 Star Wars personajlar\u0131 il\u0259 sehrli mac\u0259ralar oynay\u0131n.","Collections.curated.warhammer-pc-games.Page.Description":"Warhammer komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da strategiya, aksiyon v\u0259 RPG Warhammer oyunlar\u0131 il\u0259 qaranl\u0131q kainatda m\u00FCharib\u0259 apar\u0131n.","Collections.curated.king-pc-games.Page.Description":"King komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da King-d\u0259n Candy Crush, Farm Heroes v\u0259 daha \u00E7ox as\u0131l\u0131l\u0131q yaradan match-3 v\u0259 tapmaca oyunlar\u0131n\u0131 oynay\u0131n.","Collections.curated.big-fish-games-pc-games.Page.Description":"Big Fish komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da Windows \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn Big Fish-d\u0259n gizli obyekt, tapmaca v\u0259 rahat mac\u0259ra oyunlar\u0131 oynay\u0131n.","Collections.curated.clever-apps-universe.Page.Description":"Clever Apps Universe oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da Clever Apps-d\u0259n maraql\u0131 tapmaca, simulyasiya v\u0259 mac\u0259ra oyunlar\u0131 oynay\u0131n.","Collections.curated.g5-pc-games.Page.Description":"G5 komp\u00FCter oyunlar\u0131 \u2014 Microsoft Store-da Windows \u00FC\u00E7\u00FCn G5 Entertainment-d\u0259n gizli obyekt, match-3 v